Interface WBSResourceRoleSpreadPeriod

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ResourceAssignmentSpreadPeriodBase, SpreadPeriod, SummaryAssignmentSpreadPeriod

    public interface WBSResourceRoleSpreadPeriod
extends SummaryAssignmentSpreadPeriod
    This is a marker interface to represent a spread period that contains summarized resource or role spread data for a specific WBS.
